data.name: lblUninstallInfo.Text
data.value:
This option removes the audit system from the current database. This includes tables,stored procedures and triggers installed by AlmisAudit.All selections for user tables and columns to audit will be lost and unrecoverable unless you have made proper backups.
The existing audit log will be dropped as well. Any existing audit log data for this database will be destroyed and unrecoverable unless you have made proper backups.
